<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV85">
<l>naccarāva ṇaikkiṭanta nātapāta pōtiṉil</l>
<l>vaittacintai vāṅkuvittu nīṅkuvikka nīyiṉam</l>
<l>meyttaṉvallai yātalāla ṟintaṉaṉniṉ māyamē</l>
<l>yuyttuniṉma yakkiṉilma yakkaleṉṉai māyaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Lord who lay on the venomous serpent! I know that You are still truly capable</l>
<l>Of taking back and diverting [my] thoughts placed at [Your] lotus feet!</l>
<l>Therefore, saving [me] from your māyā,</l>
<l>Do not confuse me with Your illusion, O wonderful Lord!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
